data.description: Why wait for New Construction when you can move in NOW!? Practically New 4 bed/2.5 bath home located on almost .82 acres in growing Duncan's Crossing neighborhood. Plenty of small details to make this newly built house feel like home: New light fixtures, modern hardware, security system, and new sink to name a few. French doors lead to a cozy 1st floor office, Huge island and plenty of Counter Space in the open kitchen, Large Windows surround the bright living area! And that's just the first floor! Upstairs you'll find an open landing leading to bedrooms, hall bath, and dedicated laundry room. Owner's Suite complete with Dual Vanity, Walk in Shower, and HUGE Closet! PLUS newly added extended concrete patio in the backyard...this home has it all!
